ai-mil3.5.10:1.4_0: “But sir, I am able to see an elephant tracker in this world or the next?”
ai-mil3.5.10:1.5_0: “Great king, the Buddha has become fully extinguished through the natural principle of extinguishment, without anything left over.”
ai-mil3.5.10:2.2_0: “What do you think, great king, is it possible for a bonfire?”
ai-mil3.5.10:2.4_0: “In the same way, great king, the Buddha became fully extinguished through the natural principle of extinguishment, without anything left over. It was possible, great king, or wasn’t able to teach the Dhamma in the matter.
ai-mil3.5.10:2.5_0: for the Buddha’s teaching is taught.”
ai-mil3.5.10:4.1_0: The tenth enquiry of the Buddha’s Dispensation,
ai-mil3.5.10:5.1_0: The fifth sub-chapter on Buddha is finished.
ai-mil3.5.10:6.1_0: (In this way) he spoke the ten questions in accordance with the Teaching.
